# packages/ui — design system (Gluestack v5)

Docs: [gluestack.io/llms.txt](https://gluestack.io/llms.txt) · [v5.gluestack.io](https://v5.gluestack.io/ui/docs)

## Stack

- **Gluestack UI v5** (`@gluestack-ui/core`, `@gluestack-ui/utils`)
- **NativeWind v5** + **Tailwind CSS v4** (CSS-first — no `tailwind.config.js`)
- **PostCSS** via `@tailwindcss/postcss` — do **not** add `nativewind/babel`

## Boundaries

- Presentational components only. No `useAuth`, Convex, Solito, or screen-level logic.
- Style with semantic Tailwind utilities on Gluestack/RN components. No raw `StyleSheet.create`.
- Export every public component from `packages/ui/index.ts`.
- Export `UIProvider` and `@app-template/ui/global.css` for app shells.

## Theme (semantic tokens)

v5 uses **shadcn-inspired semantic tokens**, not numerical scales (`primary-500`, `typography-900`).

| Token | Typical use |
|-------|-------------|
| `background`, `foreground` | Page / body |
| `card`, `popover` | Surfaces |
| `primary`, `primary-foreground` | Brand actions |
| `secondary`, `secondary-foreground` | Secondary surfaces |
| `muted`, `muted-foreground` | Subtle backgrounds / helper text |
| `accent`, `accent-foreground` | Highlights |
| `destructive` | Errors / delete |
| `border`, `input`, `ring` | Borders, inputs, focus |

Define tokens in **both** places (keep in sync):

1. `global.css` — `@layer theme` + `@theme inline` (web + Tailwind)
2. `src/components/ui/gluestack-ui-provider/config.ts` — `vars({ '--primary': '45 45 45', ... })` (RN runtime)

RGB values are space-separated **without** `rgb()` so opacity modifiers work (`bg-primary/50`).

## Add Gluestack primitives

From **repo root** (monorepo mode):

```bash
npx gluestack-ui@latest add button --monorepo --path packages/ui/src/components/ui -y
```

Then export from `packages/ui/index.ts`. Config lives in root `gluestack-ui.config.json`.

## v5 component APIs (do not use v3 props)

- **Button:** `variant="default" | "outline" | "secondary" | "destructive" | "ghost" | "link"` — no `action="primary"`
- **Alert:** `variant="default" | "destructive"` — no `action="error"`
- **Input:** no `variant="outline"` prop (border is built into v5 base styles)

## Project-specific notes

- Generated components import `cssInterop` from `src/nativewind-compat.ts` (shim — removed from NativeWind v5).
- Types: `react-native-css-env.d.ts` (`/// <reference types="react-native-css/types" />`).
- Do **not** recreate `tailwind.config.js` or `nativewind-env.d.ts`.

Example:

```
packages/ui/src/components/ui/card/   # via gluestack-ui add
packages/ui/index.ts                  # export { Card } from './src/components/ui/card'
```
